desc
@Source to first 1.3 release
@


1.11
log
@Calls DISABLE and ENABLE macros with ExecBase in A6 to ensure
reliable disabling/enabling of interrupts.
@
text
@
	TTL '$Id: begin.asm,v 1.10 91/05/30 21:21:28 bryce Exp $'

